    "synth_pr": "\n## Title: Fix PUCCH configuration cloning inconsistency\n\n### Summary\nThere's an inconsistency in how PUCCH configuration is handled in the NR MAC gNB code. The `clone_pucch_configcommon()` function works correctly but is used inconsistently with manual construction approaches in other parts of the codebase. This can lead to unexpected behavior when the function is called directly.\n\nThis fix adds safety checks and consistency to ensure the function behaves predictably in all contexts.\n\n### Changes\n- `openair2/LAYER2/NR_MAC_gNB/nr_radio_config.c`: Enhanced `clone_pucch_configcommon()` with validation checks and added consistency validation after function calls\n"
}